173
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:34,880
Well, then, how come
you’re not answering her call?

174
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:35,920
I’m sick of her.

175
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:36,440
What?

176
00:16:40,040 --> 00:16:43,360
Every time she sees me, she brings me
another problem to solve.

177
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:46,320
Never bothers to show her face
when things are good.

178
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:48,760
What the hell, dude?

179
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:50,400
Why are you being so mean?

180
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:56,040
That’s what siblings do,
solving each other’s issues.

181
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:56,920
That’s how it is!

182
00:16:58,040 --> 00:17:00,160
Don’t you appreciate the fact
that she thinks of you at all?

183
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,120
Look at me.

184
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:05,040
Nobody ever gives a damn
enough to even think of me.

185
00:17:05,280 --> 00:17:08,160
I’m useless even to my own sister.

186
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,040
That’s way more awful than your situation.

187
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:15,280
