209
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:45,800
I’m sorry.

210
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:50,240
I know it’s hard.

211
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:56,080
But your being Wu is still
freaking awesome to me.

212
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:04,600
Let me know if you need help
defeating yao again.

213
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,280
I’m here for you.

214
